Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.30,0:00:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格拉齐埃斯的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.38,0:00:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.09,0:00:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.60,0:00:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exile明明不是为战争准备的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.58,0:00:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.60,0:00:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 无论何时Exile都在战火的中心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.51,0:00:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这天空的另一端
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.42,0:00:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不也在围着Exile战斗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.84,0:02:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial}Second adjourment
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.26,0:02:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在普莱斯提尔——
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.32,0:02:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们过去生活的人造星球上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.41,0:02:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个国家间战火不息
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.76,0:02:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一方是安纳托雷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.55,0:02:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一方是度西斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.53,0:02:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公会则负责调停与管理
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.78,0:02:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在将两国隔开的Grand Stream的中间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.90,0:02:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exile在等待到临之时 不停徘徊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.78,0:03:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,静待回归的移民船
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.40,0:03:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道这一真相的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.99,0:03:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将之奉若神明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.76,0:03:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它的钥匙就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.97,0:03:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾尔维斯·汉密尔顿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.53,0:03:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从得到了Exile
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.53,0:03:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要君临世界的公会手中逃了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.76,0:03:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被当作货物运走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.46,0:03:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你能接下任务
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.43,0:03:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7颗星！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.09,0:03:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,货物…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.72,0:03:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.79,0:03:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子就是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.37,0:03:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vanship驾驶员 克劳斯·沃卡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.81,0:03:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此接下拉尔夫·温斯蒂的神圣任务
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.71,0:03:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪物！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.25,0:04:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个… 我是克劳斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.02,0:04:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是拉薇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.97,0:04:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.84,0:04:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你熟睡的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.43,0:04:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经完成工作交接了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.73,0:04:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们二人是Vanship驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.79,0:04:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是空中投递员
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.18,0:04:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜欢他们俩了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.28,0:04:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇最初有点吓人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.56,0:04:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是拉薇做的三明治非常好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.18,0:04:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬塔…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.87,0:04:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬塔她…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.68,0:04:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实已经不在了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.88,0:04:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.90,0:05:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.05,0:05:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开艾尔！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.89,0:05:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.21,0:05:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银之战舰舰长——艾利克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.38,0:05:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的收货人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.61,0:05:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本该与克劳斯他们就此分别
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.02,0:05:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪奥殿下 准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.67,0:05:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之后 我们来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.98,0:05:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪奥殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.16,0:05:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露西奥拉 尸体是不会说话的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.00,0:05:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你… 是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.86,0:06:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这无趣的战场上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.83,0:06:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,独一无二的英麦曼闪闪发光
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.62,0:06:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来教你在天空飞翔的真正方法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.35,0:06:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样会不会太接近了点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.74,0:06:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为我是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.29,0:06:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是迪奥首长哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.68,0:06:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.14,0:06:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.60,0:06:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候才能再见面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.87,0:06:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机会快得出乎意料
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.29,0:06:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在Horizon Cave举办的Vanship八小时拉力赛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.03,0:07:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳斯 功率最大了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.29,0:07:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.89,0:07:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪奥殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.66,0:07:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速度不能再提高点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.59,0:07:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法再提高了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.32,0:07:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为燃料加太满了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.39,0:07:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那露西奥拉你下去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.02,0:07:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.49,0:07:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.51,0:07:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.29,0:07:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.20,0:07:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.14,0:07:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要办个聚会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.49,0:07:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聚会啊 真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.45,0:07:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟着英麦曼 结果成了俘虏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.39,0:07:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我就是为此而来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.57,0:07:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是俘虏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.43,0:07:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天快要亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.66,0:08:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.92,0:08:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.19,0:08:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁叫你那么奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.39,0:08:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.42,0:08:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给克劳斯起了个奇怪的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.76,0:08:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英麦曼就是英麦曼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.36,0:08:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳斯是克劳斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.55,0:08:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你则是艾尔维斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.60,0:08:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.46,0:08:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道好多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.67,0:08:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我给你念首诗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.45,0:08:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.26,0:08:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么诗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.33,0:08:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空另一端 存在的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.37,0:08:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.36,0:08:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.93,0:08:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带领迷路的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.40,0:08:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到母亲怀里的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.84,0:08:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exile
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.69,0:09:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要启动Exile
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.68,0:09:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要艾尔维斯与谜诗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.51,0:09:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长你知道几句啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.70,0:09:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两句吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.38,0:09:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 三句啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.45,0:09:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾利克斯的目的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.79,0:09:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.81,0:09:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到Exile
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.53,0:09:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改变世界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.32,0:09:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将戴芬妮拉下总帅的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.15,0:09:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪奥殿下 请您冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.25,0:09:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴芬妮来啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.33,0:09:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我把它击沉！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.83,0:09:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个贱人在那里！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.75,0:09:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个总帅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.03,0:09:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴芬妮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.67,0:09:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.02,0:09:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.86,0:10:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是很顶级的水哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.45,0:10:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要珍惜着喝哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.39,0:10:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.95,0:10:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的礼物是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.41,0:10:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是用旧的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.33,0:10:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英麦曼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.70,0:10:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有蛋糕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.62,0:10:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪奥你吃吃看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.05,0:10:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了你们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.68,0:10:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次感到了过生日真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.45,0:10:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}不好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.02,0:10:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}真好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.27,0:10:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.06,0:10:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿贡的试炼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.59,0:10:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公会的成人之日即将到来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.56,0:10:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.75,0:10:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}住手啊 希卡达
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.51,0:10:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}住手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.96,0:10:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露西奥拉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.12,0:10:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫露西奥拉过来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.94,0:10:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露西奥拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.10,0:10:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被带了回来 心灵也被摧毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.61,0:10:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.78,0:11:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真精彩啊 迪奥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.48,0:11:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾尔维斯 接下来的主角是你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.60,0:11:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.68,0:11:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么先是达格贝尔家的谜诗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.60,0:11:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将大地染成金色的波浪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.29,0:11:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哺育生命的恩泽气息
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.10,0:11:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小麦的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.07,0:11:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.91,0:11:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聚齐我和谜诗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.40,0:11:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴芬妮 得到了Exile
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.18,0:11:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仪式结束后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.85,0:11:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪奥的心灵并未回来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.17,0:12:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露西奥拉拯救了丧心的迪奥与我们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.61,0:12:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露西奥拉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.38,0:12:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一个人要去做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.24,0:12:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去除掉那些要加害迪奥殿下的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.87,0:12:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一无所知地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.61,0:12:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘记了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.10,0:12:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太精彩了 露西奥拉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.35,0:12:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要赏你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.38,0:12:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请还迪奥殿下自由
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.48,0:13:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 把这个拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.23,0:13:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么要放走我心爱的迪奥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.51,0:13:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.48,0:13:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪啊 你们又不是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.19,0:13:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露西奥拉是迪奥的什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.27,0:13:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.92,0:13:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.90,0:13:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃的时候要露出好吃的表情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.85,0:13:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表情？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.24,0:13:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.17,0:13:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和露西奥拉是朋友哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.70,0:13:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是迪奥殿下的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.63,0:13:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.15,0:14:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很美
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.40,0:14:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很美哦 露西奥拉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.13,0:14:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,节流阀 确认
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.04,0:14:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全盘检查 Clear
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.94,0:14:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启动引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.20,0:14:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.74,0:14:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.22,0:14:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你好运 克劳斯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.02,0:14:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿顺风与你同在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.79,0:14:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们再次前往Grand Stream
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.27,0:14:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了从戴芬妮手中抢回Exile
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.38,0:14:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前来追击我们的是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.82,0:14:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混乱中的迪奥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.53,0:15:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1点钟方向有雨侯鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.39,0:15:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到终点了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.56,0:15:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露西奥拉 要输了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.05,0:15:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速度不能再提高些吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.12,0:15:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露西奥拉 你下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.57,0:15:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.21,0:15:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到终点啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.68,0:15:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.73,0:15:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我们的胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.01,0:15:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们击败英麦曼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.51,0:15:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露西奥拉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.04,0:15:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露西奥拉…？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.86,0:15:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为我叫你下去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.04,0:15:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为我叫你下去吗 露西奥拉…！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.17,0:15:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳斯 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.56,0:15:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我搞不清楚方向了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.73,0:16:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为我们的陛下开一条路！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.87,0:16:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全舰 开始射击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.46,0:16:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exile放出数不清的触手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.99,0:16:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定时信管鱼雷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.24,0:16:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备全部发射
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.89,0:16:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.46,0:16:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开1至3号主炮塔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.55,0:16:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标 我方战舰乌尔巴努斯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.66,0:16:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船员退到船前方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.77,0:16:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.80,0:16:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.87,0:16:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,航向仰角20度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.73,0:17:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引擎全开 最大航速
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.31,0:17:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下 击败总帅！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.59,0:17:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口径渐减式重高射炮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.53,0:17:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.78,0:17:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从戴芬妮舰上听到了舰长的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.95,0:17:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞向天空…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.88,0:17:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳斯 两点钟方向能看见光
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.58,0:17:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用加速装置
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.99,0:17:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.64,0:18:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grand Stream
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.30,0:18:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被我们穿过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.16,0:18:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.37,0:18:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.03,0:18:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是度西斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.89,0:18:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带我去Exile那里 克劳斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.75,0:18:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.51,0:18:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.73,0:18:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.56,0:18:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你终于穿过Grand Stream了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.80,0:19:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.71,0:19:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.51,0:19:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空另一端 存在的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.63,0:19:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带领迷路的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.40,0:19:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到母亲怀里的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.87,0:19:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exile
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.38,0:19:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将大地染成金色的波浪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.90,0:19:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哺育生命的恩泽气息
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.88,0:19:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小麦的大地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.79,0:19:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使下凡之路
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.22,0:19:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是巨大的圣风之路
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.28,0:19:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grand Stream
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.64,0:19:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记忆的另一端存在的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.85,0:20:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.21,0:20:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诞生与回归的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.58,0:20:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝色的星球
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.12,0:21:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.00,0:22:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们曾发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.02,0:22:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创造一个不分安纳托雷 度西斯与公会
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.57,0:22:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有纷争的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.74,0:22:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 却又爆发了战争
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.26,0:22:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论去哪里都会被盯上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.41,0:22:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被利用
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.44,0:22:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤害别人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.73,0:22:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我这种人干脆…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.25,0:22:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾尔维斯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.09,0:22:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得为什么你在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.40,0:22:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你和大家紧紧地连在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.39,0:22:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 我的命也如此
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.76,0:23:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以活下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.90,0:23:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要活下去 痛苦地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.24,0:23:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪奥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.19,0:23:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.32,0:23:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快起来 瞌睡虫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.27,0:23:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 去吃午饭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.93,0:23:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾尔由我保护
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.04,0:23:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我和英麦曼约定好了
